            <button class="pdpv9-stories__play" aria-label="Emily R. video" type="button"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M5 3v14l13-7L5 3z" fill="currentColor"/></svg></button>
          </div>
          <div class="pdpv9-stories__caption"><strong>Emily R., 39</strong> · San Francisco, CA<br><span>"Down 12 lbs in 8 weeks. The 4PM ritual is non-negotiable now."</span></div>
